      • createConfigDoc

        protected org.w3c.dom.Document createConfigDoc​(AVList params)
        Returns a Layer configuration document which describes the tiled imagery produced by this TiledImageProducer. The document's contents are based on the configuration document for a TiledImageLayer, except this document describes an offline dataset. This returns null if the parameter list is null, or if the configuration document cannot be created for any reason.
        Specified by:
        createConfigDoc in class TiledRasterProducer
        Parameters:
        params - the parameters which describe a Layer configuration document's contents.
        Returns:
        the configuration document, or null if the parameter list is null or does not contain the required parameters.
